{"results":[{"aya":"015","id":5434,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"难道你们没有看到真主怎样创造7层天，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"016","id":5435,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"并以月亮为光明，以太阳为明灯吗？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"017","id":5436,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"真主使你们从大地生长出来，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"018","id":5437,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"然后使你们再返於大地，然后，又把你们从大地取出来。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"019","id":5438,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"真主为你们而平展大地，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"020","id":5439,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"以便你们在大地上走著宽阔的道路。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"021","id":5440,"locale":"zh","sura":"071","text":"努哈说：我的主啊！他们确已违抗我，他们顺从那因财产和子嗣而更加亏折的人们，","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":4,"previousPage":"/zh/s071-2.json","nextPage":"/zh/s071-4.json"}}